.SH NAME
mpt3sas_scsih_expander_find_by_sas_address \- expander device search
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct _sas_node *" mpt3sas_scsih_expander_find_by_sas_address
.BI "(struct MPT3SAS_ADAPTER *ioc "  ","
.BI "u64 sas_address "  ","
.BI "struct hba_port *port "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ioc" 12
per adapter object
.IP "sas_address" 12
sas address
.IP "port" 12
hba port entry
.SH "CONTEXT"
Calling function should acquire ioc->sas_node_lock.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This searches for expander device based on sas_address & port number,
then returns the sas_node object.
